Name: Moorhuhn: Tiger and Chicken
About the game: The Crazy Chicken first saw the light of day 17 years ago, and has been on lots of adventures since then. Now it's back to face its biggest challenge yet: In Crazy Chicken: Tiger & Chicken, you play the hero in a fast-paced story filled with terrifying enemies and dramatic combat. As a Shaolin fighter, you must liberate your oppressed people and save the love of your life. Features Action RPG for the whole family Fight with a variety of weapons Sophisticated skill system Beautiful 3D graphics Supports controllers
